@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hvavgq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v1
    v2 = wp.sin(0.66)
    v0 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.86 - v0 + 0.60)) * wp.cos(0.83))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.abs(v2 + 0.12)))
    v0 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.47 * v0 + 0.65) / (v2 + 0.31 / v1 + 0.56)))
    data[tid] = v0
